    "name": "爆弹英雄",
    "steam_appid": 2220480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速游戏，轻松上手</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一场战斗只需10分钟左右，让你随时随地都能体验到紧张刺激的战斗。简单的操作让你轻松上手，享受无尽的爽快感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/62a2fabad1b2b055004a44725e963e63.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/62a2fabad1b2b055004a44725e963e63.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/62a2fabad1b2b055004a44725e963e63.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/ceb702769200a55ed8d4c519ccaf096f.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/ceb702769200a55ed8d4c519ccaf096f.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/ceb702769200a55ed8d4c519ccaf096f.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多样的英雄选择</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有众多技能各异的英雄供你选择，每个英雄都拥有独特的游戏体验。找到最适合你的角色，领略各种战斗风格。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/d198f74d7e96a0fb043a1f03bce91dc0.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/d198f74d7e96a0fb043a1f03bce91dc0.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/d198f74d7e96a0fb043a1f03bce91dc0.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的武器系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任何武器可以发射任何子弹，不同的武器拥有不同的弹药量、射击速度和枪口数等。子弹也各具特色，飞行弹道、子弹伤害和攻击特效各不相同。上千种组合让你打造出个性化的武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/0c5de11cc69cc1e195c3039311322d83.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/0c5de11cc69cc1e195c3039311322d83.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/0c5de11cc69cc1e195c3039311322d83.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略性的卡牌系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的卡牌构筑可以强化玩家的能力，不同的卡牌策略将带来不用的游戏体验。主打子弹穿透，还是范围伤害，或者组建一支无人机大军？尽情探索吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/b69d928f334a9f5551e235cbd211b4d3.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/b69d928f334a9f5551e235cbd211b4d3.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/b69d928f334a9f5551e235cbd211b4d3.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的关卡挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个游戏关卡都拥有不同的地图机制和敌人，敌人各具特色，拥有独特的技能。20个进阶难度等你挑战，每一级都会叠加一个难度选项，让你永不厌倦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/7b276a9f2e893766011bb81199cce012.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/7b276a9f2e893766011bb81199cce012.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/7b276a9f2e893766011bb81199cce012.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/b4f146d03076524dcf36df8b02265a7d.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/b4f146d03076524dcf36df8b02265a7d.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/b4f146d03076524dcf36df8b02265a7d.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/0d1e6538ca6b8c4f18eed9a67bdf05bb.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/0d1e6538ca6b8c4f18eed9a67bdf05bb.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/0d1e6538ca6b8c4f18eed9a67bdf05bb.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的收藏要素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集扭蛋币，解锁新的英雄、武器、子弹和卡牌。随着游戏的进行，游戏内容将不断丰富，给你带来更多的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/caf825f41d19555e6b940488886f9026.poster.avif?t=1741614871\" width=640 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/caf825f41d19555e6b940488886f9026.webm?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/caf825f41d19555e6b940488886f9026.mp4?t=1741614871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通关技巧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1、时刻查看商店，购买和升级卡牌强化自己。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2、看到合适的卡牌可以锁定商店，避免每分钟的刷新替换。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3、在没有压力的情况下优先升级商店，可以购买更强力的卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4、卡组上限只有8张，提前规划好卡牌构筑。</p>",
